Before you export annotations, please set corresponding params in keep_in_mind.rb:
<code>
TODO_LIST_ID  = '5921990'
TODO_LIST_URL = 'http://unigate.basecamphq.com/todo_lists'
USER = 'user'
PASSWORD = 'password'
</code>

To export annotations into your Basecamp todo list just run:
<code>rake notes:export</code>

You can add rake invocation into crontab:
<code>5 12 * * * sh -c 'cd ~/www/project && rake notes:export'</code>
